# 💰 Smart Finance Tracker

A full-stack **MERN Stack** web application that helps users efficiently manage their personal finances by tracking income, expenses, budgets, and savings goals through a secure and user-friendly platform.

---

# 📌 Project Overview

Smart Finance Tracker is a web-based financial management system developed using the **MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, and Node.js (MERN)** stack. The application enables users to securely manage their financial records, monitor spending, set budgets, create savings goals, and analyze their financial performance using interactive dashboards and reports.

The project replaces traditional manual financial record-keeping with a centralized digital platform that provides real-time financial tracking and secure data management.

---

# ✨ Features

### 🔐 User Authentication

* User Registration
* User Login
* JWT Authentication
* Password Encryption
* Secure Session Management

### 📊 Dashboard

* Total Income Summary
* Total Expense Summary
* Current Balance
* Budget Usage Tracking
* Savings Goal Overview
* Interactive Charts
* Recent Transactions

### 💵 Income Management

* Add Income
* View Income History
* Delete Income
* Track Total Income
* Manage Income Sources

### 💸 Expense Management

* Add Expenses
* Categorize Expenses
* View Expense History
* Track Total Expenses
* Spending Analysis

### 💼 Budget Management

* Set Budget Limits
* Monitor Budget Usage
* Budget Status
* Overspending Alerts
* Budget Summary

### 🎯 Savings Goal Management

* Create Savings Goals
* Set Target Amount
* Track Goal Progress
* Goal Completion Status
* Balance Availability Check

### 📈 Analytics & Reports

* Expense Distribution Charts
* Income Source Charts
* Monthly Spending Reports
* Financial Analytics Dashboard
* PDF Report Generation

