# 📊 Existing System

Traditional financial management methods rely on manual records, spreadsheets, or notebooks, which often result in:

* Manual calculations
* Data entry errors
* No centralized storage
* Lack of real-time tracking
* No financial analytics
* Risk of data loss

---

# ✅ Proposed System

Smart Finance Tracker provides:

* Centralized financial management
* Real-time income and expense tracking
* Budget monitoring
* Savings goal management
* Interactive dashboards
* Financial reports
* Secure authentication using JWT
* Password encryption

---

# ⚙️ Installation

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Hrithika-B/Smart-Finance-Tracker.git
```

## Install Backend

```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Install Frontend

```bash
cd finance-app
npm install
npm start
```

